call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Hield (SAC) throws an errant pass that goes out of bounds.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact to Ball's (NOP) arm at the end of his drive, but the contact does not affect his ability to make his intended pass.
Favors (NOP) receives the pass and takes two legal steps after he gathers.  He then maintains his pivot foot.
Holmes (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Favors (NOP) and makes clean ball contact on his steal attempt.
Favors (NOP) is in the lane for more than 3 seconds.
Hart (NOP) does not maintain a legal vertical position when he makes contact to Fox's (SAC) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Barnes (SAC) and Favors (NOP) engage and separate as Favors cuts down the lane to the basket.
Holiday (NOP) and Hield (SAC) engage and disengage as they come around the screen.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (NOP) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ball (NOP) makes marginal contact to Holmes' (SAC) back during the rebound, but Holmes' is able to get to the ball and attempt a tip-in.
As the shot is in the air, Holiday (NOP) pushes Hield (SAC) in the back and the contact dislodges him into Fox (SAC), affecting his ability to land safely from his jump shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Ingram (NOP).
Favors (NOP) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hart (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Barnes (SAC).
Favors (NOP) is slightly late when he establishes himself in a screening position in Joseph's (SAC) path, but the contact is marginal.
Holmes (SAC) clamps Favors' (NOP) arm and impedes his ability to get to the ball during the rebound.
Favors (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Hield (SAC).
Hart (NOP) makes marginal contact to Holmes' (SAC) body during his putback layup at the rim.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Holiday (NOP).
Ingram (NOP) makes contact to Bjelica's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Favors (NOP) moves into Ariza (SAC) and delivers contact on his screen that dislodges Ariza from his legal guarding position.
Holmes (SAC) makes a slight brush against Redick's (NOP) arm prior to him gathering and beginning his upward shooting motion.
